rows.label: tlk45300011_05_msg0001
rows.name: Could I ask a favor of you?

rows.label: tlk45300011_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Thing is, we just received a huge
delivery from Superbia.

rows.label: tlk45300011_05_msg0003
rows.name:
It's much bigger than usual, so we're
behind schedule handling it all.

rows.label: tlk45300011_05_msg0004
rows.name: That's why I need your help.

rows.label: tlk45300011_05_msg0005
rows.name:
If any of those Blades you've got thinks
they're strong enough, could they help
out with lugging the stuff?

rows.label: tlk45300011_05_msg0007
rows.name:
Might even be able to make up
for lost time if things go well.
